Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.07,0:22:34.04,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(152,152)\blur1}人は　なんで？なんで？　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.08,0:22:37.83,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(152,152)\blur1}何度　傷ついても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.92,0:22:44.21,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(152,152)\blur1}恋に落ちる生き物なの
